T16TD4410E:346a-3: bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
T16TD4410E:346a-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4410E:346a-5: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' ba gser gyi ri bo 'dra //
T16TD4410E:346a-6: 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon po dri ma gsum spangs pa //
T16TD4410E:346a-7: sangs rgyas padma rgyas pa'i 'dab 'dra'i spyan mnga' ba //
T16TD4410E:346a-8: bkra shis des ni skye dgu zhi byed dang po'o //
T16TD4410E:346a-9: de yis nye bar bstan pa'i mchog rab mi g-yo ba //
T16TD4410E:346a-10: 'jig rten gsum na grags shing lha dang mis mchod pa //
T16TD4410E:346a-11: chos kyi dam pa skye dgu rnams la zhi byed pa //
T16TD4410E:346a-12: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
T16TD4410E:346b-0: dge 'dun dam pa'i chos ldan thos pa'i bkra shis phyug / mi @346b dang lha dang lha ma yin gyis mchod pa'i gnas //
T16TD4410E:346b-1: tshogs kyi mchog rab ngo tsha shes dang dpal gyi gzhi //
T16TD4410E:346b-2: de ni 'jig rten dge ba'i bkra shis gsum pa'o //
T16TD4410E:346b-3: sems can kun la phan phyir byang chub mnga' ba po //
T16TD4410E:346b-4: don rnams thams cad 'grub par brtul ba yongs ldan pa //
T16TD4410E:346b-5: tshogs kyi lam dgyes thung ba'i bkra shis gang byung ba //
T16TD4410E:346b-6: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /'gro la phan phyir de bzhin gshegs pa dga' ldan lha'i //
T16TD4410E:346b-7: gzhal med khang gi snying po nas ni 'dir gshegs te //
T16TD4410E:346b-8: dbang bcas lha yis bskor ba'i bkra shis gang byung ba //
T16TD4410E:346b-9: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / lo ma me tog 'od 'bar nyams dga' lumbi'i tshal //
T16TD4410E:346b-10: lha mang dag gis bsten par mgon po bltams pa na //
T16TD4410E:346b-11: srid pa'i mthar phyin pa yi bkra shis gang byung ba //
T16TD4410E:346b-12: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / grong khyer ser skya'i gnas nas rgyal po'i pho brang du //
T16TD4410E:346b-13: lhums nas bltams pa ston pa bde gshegs zas gtsang sras //
T16TD4410E:346b-14: myur bskrun bdud rtsi'i chus gtor ba yi bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:346b-15: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / grong khyer dam pa ser skya'i gnas zhes bya bar ni //
T16TD4410E:346b-16: rmad du grags pa che ba'i lha yis mngon bstod pa //
T16TD4410E:346b-17: bsam yas dge sgrub bsod nams phung po'i bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:346b-18: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / dgyes shing nam phyed grong khyer mchog nas mngon byung ste //
T16TD4410E:346b-19: dka' thub tshal du mngon par gshegs shing tshangs la sogs //
T16TD4410E:346b-20: lha yi tshogs kyis yongs su bskor ba'i bkra shis gang ;
T16TD4410E:346b-21: / bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / rab tu 'od 'bar gser dang 'dra ba'i sku mnga' zhing //
T16TD4410E:346b-22: bee d'urya ltar sngo ba'i rtsva bting steng bzhugs te //
T16TD4410E:346b-23: skyil mo krung bcas mi g-yo mchog gi bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:346b-24: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / chu bo'i 'gram na tsa sha'i phreng gis yongs bskor ba //
T16TD4410E:346b-25: shin tu rmad du byung ba'i sred pa sel mdzad pa //
T16TD4410E:346b-26: klu yi rgyal pos phyag byas pa yi bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:346b-27: bkra shes des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / shing rgyal drung gshegs byams pa'i stobs kyis bdud kyi phyogs //
T16TD4410E:347a-0: mang po btul te sa steng dang ni nam @347a * //
T16TD4410E:347a-2: bcom ldan bkra shis rnam pa sna tshogs gang byung ba //
T16TD4410E:347a-3: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / sdug bsngal mtha' dag gzhig phyir rdo rje'i gdan bzhugs te //
T16TD4410E:347a-4: nams kyi tho rangs bdud bzhi po dag rnam btul ba //
T16TD4410E:347a-5: ston pa bde bar gshegs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-6: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / grong khyer b'a r'a na s'ir drang srong mchog bzhugs nas //
T16TD4410E:347a-7: chos kyi 'khor lo mchog bstan pa yi bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:347a-8: lha yul ding 'dir shin tu rmad du byung gyur pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-9: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / bkra shis gang zhig phan byed dam pa dag byed pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-10: bsod nams dag byed 'phags pa'i skye bos mngon bstod pa /
T16TD4410E:347a-11: bcom ldan sh'akya thub pa'i seng ges gang gsungs pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-12: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / mu stegs byed pa rnams kyis nga rgyal gzhom pa dang //
T16TD4410E:347a-13: 'gro la bde ba bskyed phyir cho 'phrul dam pa dag / nye bar ston pa rgyal ba'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-14: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog /'gro la phan phyir mtho ris nas ni 'dir gshegs te //
T16TD4410E:347a-15: tshangs pa la sogs lha tshogs lag na rnga yab gdugs //
T16TD4410E:347a-16: sna tshogs thogs pas yongs su bskor ba'i bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:347a-17: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / de bzhin gshegs pa zhi ba mchog tu nyer gshegs pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-18: mand'a ra ba'i me tog mang pos mngon mchod pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-19: lha mchog rnams kyis mngon par bstod pa'i bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:347a-20: bkra shis des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / lha dbang klu dang mi yi dbang pos phyag byas pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-21: mkha' lding gnod sbyin dri zi'i dbang pos mchod gyur pa //
T16TD4410E:347a-22: de bzhin gshegs pa'i stobs bcu ldan pa'i bkra shis gang //
T16TD4410E:347a-23: bkra shes des ni skye dgu rnams la zhi byed shog / dkon mchog gsum dang mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa slob dpon 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4410E:347a-25: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang /
T16TD4410E:347a-26: zhu chen gyi lo ts'a ba bande ye shes sdes bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa//
